description.en: Keep it wholesome brand. Raising awareness about mental health, while creating a growing community of people spreading the message of hope to those that need it. 20% of all profits are donated to charities specializing in mental illness research, supporting those with anxiety depression, or other mental health issues.
description.ga_IE: Coinnigh é branda folláin.Feasacht a ardú faoi mheabhairshláinte, agus pobal atá ag fás de dhaoine atá ag leathadh an teachtaireacht a bhfuil súil acu leo siúd a bhfuil gá acu leo.Bronntar 20% de na brabúis go léir ar charthanais a dhíríonn ar thaighde ar thinneas meabhrach, ag tacú leo siúd a bhfuil dúlagar imní orthu, nó saincheisteanna meabhairshláinte eile.
